 stores leases stores and provides engineering maintenance and logistic services for the retail complexes and retail infrastructure customers it is also involved in direct marketing of fuel to institutional customers industries and other large enterprises as well as to car fleets this division has  filling stations the paz industries and services division distributes and sells lpg for cooking heating water boiling and fueling cars and markets distributes and sells devices that consume lpg as well as converts plants to natural gas operation this division also produces recycles imports markets and exports lubricants chemicals and solvents produces markets and exports sealing and insulation products for the construction industry produces and markets products for transport infrastructure and stores markets supplies and distributes jet fuel and aviation gasoline as well as provides refueling services to aviation companies the paz refining and logistics division manages refinery imports crude oil and related products manufactures oil distillates generates and sells electricity and offers logistic services including the storage and distribution of fuels as well as purchasing and supply services the company was formerly known as shell palestine and changed its name to paz oil company limited in  paz oil company limited was founded in  and is based in yakum israel detailed description holland buildingeuro parkkibbutzyakum  israelfounded in  employees phone     fax     key executives for paz oil company ltd mr yona fogel chief executive officer age  total annual compensation m mrs sharona novak chief financial officer and vice president age  total annual compensation m mr malachi alper vp ceo of refinery  logistics division and ceo of paz ashdod refinery ltd age  total annual compensation m mr amir erez chief executive officer of pazgas ltd age  total annual compensation m hagai zohar chief executive officer of paz lubricants  chemicals ltd and chief executive officer of pazk